<h2>Order Confirmed!</h2>
<p>Hi {{name}},</p>
<p>Thank you for your order! We've received it and are getting things ready for you.</p>

<div style="background-color: #f8fafc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0;">
    <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; color: #475569;">Order Summary</p>
    <p style="margin: 8px 0 0 0; color: #64748b;">Order ID: <span style="color: #334155; font-weight: 500;">{{orderId}}</span></p>
    <p style="margin: 4px 0 0 0; color: #64748b;">Total Amount: <span style="color: #334155; font-weight: 500;">{{currency}} {{total}}</span></p>
</div>

<p>You can track your order status and view all details in your dashboard:</p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="{{trackingUrl}}" class="button">View Order Details</a>
</div>

<p>We'll notify you as soon as your items are shipped!</p>
<div class="divider"></div>
<p>Best regards,<br>The MarketX Team</p>
